      <title>桥水表示中国股票抛售使得估值具有吸引力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/bridgewater-was-bullish-on-china-stocks-after-fund-gained-11</link>
      <description><![CDATA[桥水联合投资公司(Bridgewater Associates)在中国最近一次股市崩盘前几天向投资者表示，它对中国股市“适度看好”，因为长期的暴跌使得估值具有吸引力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/bridgewater-was-bullish-on-china-stocks-after-fund-gained-11</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 03:38:20 GMT</pubDate>
