      <title>日本银行加大对日本央行今年加息的押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/japanese-banks-climb-on-bets-the-boj-will-lift-rates-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于押注日本央行今年将比预期更早结束负利率，日本银行股创下 11 月份以来的最大涨幅，从而有助于提振盈利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/japanese-banks-climb-on-bets-the-boj-will-lift-rates-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 03:20:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人民币卖空者面临因中国股市救援而遭受损失的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/yuan-short-sellers-risk-getting-burned-on-china-stocks-rescue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[人民币似乎将成为中国遏制股市暴跌计划的主要受益者，因为股市救助计划将加剧海外货币的稀缺，从而给卖空者带来压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/yuan-short-sellers-risk-getting-burned-on-china-stocks-rescue</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 03:00:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
